{
  "chapter": "096",
  "title": "张丞相列传",
  "translations": {
    "1": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张苍\">张丞相（张苍）</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张苍\">苍（张苍）</span>，是<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">阳武</span>人。喜好研习书籍、<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">律历</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>时任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">御史</span>，主管<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">柱下方书</span>。因有罪逃回家乡。等到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">沛公</span>攻略地经过<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">阳武</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张苍\">苍（张苍）</span>以客人身份跟随<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">南阳</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张苍\">苍（张苍）</span>因犯<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">法</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">当斩</span>，解开<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">衣</span>服伏在刑砧上，身材高大，肥白如<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">瓠</span>瓜，当时<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王陵</span>看见便觉此美<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>奇异，就对<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">沛公</span>说情，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">赦</span>免不<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">斩</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张苍\">苍（张苍）</span>于是跟随西进<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">武关</span>，至<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">咸阳</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">沛公</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span>为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汉王</span>，进入<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">汉中</span>，回师平定<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">三秦</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈馀</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span>走<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">常山王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张耳</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">耳</span>归附<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>于是任命<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张苍</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">常山守</span>。跟随<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">淮阴侯</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张苍\">苍（张苍）</span>俘获<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈馀</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>地平定后，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汉王</span>任<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张苍\">苍（张苍）</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">代相</span>，防备边寇。不久调任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">赵相</span>，辅佐<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">赵王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">耳</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">耳</span>卒，辅佐<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">赵王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">敖</span>。又调任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">代王</span>之相。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">燕王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">臧荼</span>反叛，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高祖</span>前去<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span>之。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张苍\">苍（张苍）</span>以<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">代相</span>身份跟随<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">臧荼</span>有功，于<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">六年</span>中封为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">北平侯</span>，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">食邑</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千二百户</span>。"
    },
    "2": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "迁为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">计相</span>，<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">一月（时长）</span>后，改以<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">列侯</span>身份任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">主计</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">四年（时长）</span>。此时<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">萧何</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相国</span>，而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张苍</span>自<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>时便是<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">柱下史</span>，熟悉<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>的<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">图书</span>计簿。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张苍\">苍（张苍）</span>又善用<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">算</span>计、<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">律历</span>，因此让<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张苍\">苍（张苍）</span>以<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">列侯</span>身份住在<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相府</span>，领管各郡国上报的计簿。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">黥布</span>反叛逃亡后，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">皇子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘长\">长（刘长）</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">淮南王</span>，由<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张苍</span>担任其国之相。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十四年</span>，升任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">御史大夫</span>。"
    },
    "3": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周昌</span>，是<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">沛</span>人。他的堂<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">兄</span>叫<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周苛</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>时都担任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">泗水卒史</span>。到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高祖</span>在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">沛</span>起兵，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">泗水守监</span>，于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周昌</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周苛</span>从<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">卒史</span>跟随<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">沛公</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">沛公</span>任<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周昌</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">职志</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周苛</span>为客卿。跟随入关，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">沛公</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span>为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汉王</span>，任<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周苛</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">御史大夫</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周昌</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">中尉</span>。"
    },
    "4": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汉王</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">四年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>军紧急<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">围</span>攻<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汉王</span>于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">荥阳</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汉王</span>突围逃出，让<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周苛</span>守卫<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">荥阳</span>城。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">荥阳</span>城，想让<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周苛</span>担任将领。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">苛</span>骂道：\"你快投降<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汉王</span>吧！否则，就要做俘虏了！\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项羽</span>发怒，烹<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周苛</span>。于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汉王</span>就<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">拜</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周昌</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">御史大夫</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周昌</span>常跟随<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：项羽\">项籍（项羽）</span>。于<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">六年</span>中与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：萧何\">萧（萧何）</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曹参\">曹（曹参）</span>等人一起受封：<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周昌</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">汾阴侯</span>；<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周苛</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周成</span>因<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">父</span>亲死于公事，封为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">高景侯</span>。"
    },
    "5": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">昌</span>为人性情刚强，敢于直言，自<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：萧何\">萧（萧何）</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曹参\">曹（曹参）</span>等都对他礼让谦卑。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">昌</span>曾在闲暇时入宫奏事，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘邦\">高帝（刘邦）</span>正搂抱<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：戚夫人\">戚姬（戚夫人）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">昌</span>回身就走，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘邦\">高帝（刘邦）</span>追上他，骑在<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周昌</span>的脖子上，问道：\"我是什么样的君主？\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">昌</span>仰头说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>就是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：夏桀\">桀（夏桀）</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：商纣\">纣（商纣）</span>那样的君主。\" 于是皇上笑他，但尤其忌惮<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周昌</span>。 等到<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">帝</span>想废<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>，而立<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：戚夫人\">戚姬（戚夫人）</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">如意</span>为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>时，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大臣</span>极力劝阻，没能奏效；皇上因<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">留侯</span>的计策才罢休。 而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周昌</span>在朝廷上强烈谏争，皇上问他的道理，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">昌</span>为人口吃，又极为愤怒，说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>口不能言，但<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>期期知道这不可以。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>即使想废<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>期期不奉诏。\" 皇上欣然而笑。 朝议罢后，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：吕雉\">吕后（吕雉）</span>在东厢房侧耳听着，见到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周昌</span>，为他下跪致谢说：\"若没有您，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>几乎被废。\""
    },
    "6": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "这以后<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：戚夫人\">戚姬（戚夫人）</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">如意</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">赵王</span>，年纪<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高祖</span>担心<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">万岁</span>之后不能保全。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">赵尧</span>年纪轻轻，任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">符玺御史</span>。 <span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>人<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">方与公</span>对<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">御史大夫</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周昌</span>说：\"您的属<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">史</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">赵尧</span>，虽然年轻，却是奇才，您必须另眼相看，这人将来会取代您的位子。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周昌</span>笑道：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">尧</span>年少，不过<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">刀笔</span>小吏罢了，怎能到那个地位！\" 过了不久，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">赵尧</span>侍奉<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高祖</span>。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高祖</span>独自心中不乐，悲歌，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">群臣</span>不知皇上为何这样。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">赵尧</span>上前请问：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>不乐，是不是因为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">赵王</span>年少而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">戚夫人</span>与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：吕雉\">吕后（吕雉）</span>有嫌隙？担心<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">万岁</span>之后<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">赵王</span>不能自保？\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高祖</span>说：\"是的。我私下忧虑，不知如何是好。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">尧</span>说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>应当独为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">赵王</span>设置一位尊贵强势的相，这个人须是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：吕雉\">吕后（吕雉）</span>、<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>、<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">群臣</span>一向敬重畏惧的，才可以。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高祖</span>说：\"是啊。我也想这样，可是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">群臣</span>中有谁能胜任呢？\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">尧</span>说：\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">御史大夫</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周昌</span>，他为人坚忍耿直，而且自<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：吕雉\">吕后（吕雉）</span>、<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>及<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大臣</span>都一向敬重畏惧他。只有<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">昌</span>可以。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高祖</span>说：\"好。\" 于是就召见<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周昌</span>，对他说：\"我想再麻烦您一次，您务必为我做<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">赵王</span>的相。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周昌</span>哭着说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>从起兵就跟从<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>为什么中途把<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>抛弃给<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>呢？\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高祖</span>说：\"我很清楚这是降用，但我私下忧心<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">赵王</span>，想来想去除您没有人可以。您不得已就勉强去吧！\" 于是调<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">御史大夫</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周昌</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">赵相</span>。"
    },
    "7": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "过了很久，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高祖</span>拿着<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">御史大夫印</span>玩弄，说：\"谁可以担任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">御史大夫</span>？\" 仔细打量<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">赵尧</span>，说：\"没有人能取代<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">尧</span>。\" 于是<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">拜</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">赵尧</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">御史大夫</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">尧</span>以前就有军功食邑，又以<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">御史大夫</span>身份跟随<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈豨</span>有功，封为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">江邑侯</span>。"
    },
    "8": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高祖</span>崩，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：吕雉\">吕太后（吕雉）</span>派使者召<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">赵王</span>，其相<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周昌</span>让<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">赵王</span>称病不去。使者往返三次，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周昌</span>坚持不遣<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">赵王</span>。于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：吕雉\">高后（吕雉）</span>以此为患，就派使者召<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周昌</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周昌</span>到后，拜见<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：吕雉\">高后（吕雉）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：吕雉\">高后（吕雉）</span>怒骂<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周昌</span>说：\"你难道不知道我怨恨<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">戚氏</span>吗？却不遣送<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">赵王</span>，为何？\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">昌</span>既被征召，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：吕雉\">高后（吕雉）</span>又派使者召<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">赵王</span>，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">赵王</span>果然来了。到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">长安</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">一个多月（时长）</span>，饮<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">药</span>而死。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周昌</span>因而称病不<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">朝见</span>，过<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">三年（时长）</span>而死。"
    },
    "9": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "过了<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">五年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：吕雉\">高后（吕雉）</span>听说<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">御史大夫</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">江邑侯</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">赵尧</span>当年在<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高祖</span>时出谋保全<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">赵王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">如意</span>，就给<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">尧</span>定罪，用<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">广阿侯</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">任敖</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">御史大夫</span>。"
    },
    "10": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">任敖</span>，原是<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">沛</span>县的狱吏。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高祖</span>曾躲避官吏，官吏就把<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：吕雉\">吕后（吕雉）</span>拘押起来，待她不恭谨。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">任敖</span>一向与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高祖</span>友好，发怒，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span>伤了主管<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：吕雉\">吕后（吕雉）</span>的官吏。到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高祖</span>初起兵时，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">敖</span>以客卿身份跟随，做<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">御史</span>，守<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">丰</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">二年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高祖</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span>为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汉王</span>，东进<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：项羽\">项籍（项羽）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">敖</span>升为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">上党守</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈豨</span>反叛时，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">敖</span>坚守，封为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">广阿侯</span>，食<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千八百户</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：吕雉\">高后（吕雉）</span>时做<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">御史大夫</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">三年（时长）</span>后免职，以<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">平阳侯</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">曹窋</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">御史大夫</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：吕雉\">高后（吕雉）</span>崩，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">曹窋</span>与<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大臣</span>共同<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕禄</span>等。免职后，以<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">淮南相</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张苍</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">御史大夫</span>。"
    },
    "11": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张苍\">苍（张苍）</span>与<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">绛侯</span>等尊奉<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">代王</span>为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉文帝\">孝文皇帝（汉文帝）</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">四年</span>，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">灌婴</span>去世，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张苍</span>升为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>。"
    },
    "12": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "自<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>朝兴起至<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝文</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">二十多年（时长）</span>，正值<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>初定，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">将相</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">公卿</span>都是<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">军吏</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张苍</span>做<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">计相</span>时，整理匡正<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">律历</span>。因<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高祖</span>于<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十月</span>开始到达<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">霸上</span>，沿袭<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>时以<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十月</span>为岁首的做法，没有更改。推演<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">五德之运</span>，认为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>当处<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">水德</span>之时，仍崇尚黑色。他吹<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">律</span>调<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">乐</span>，纳入音声之中，并据此确定<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">律令</span>。至于百工事务，都为<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>制定规程。到他出任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>，最终完成这些事，所以<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>家谈论<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">律历</span>的，都以<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张苍</span>为根本。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张苍\">苍（张苍）</span>本好读书，无所不观，无所不通，尤精<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">律历</span>。"
    },
    "13": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张苍</span>感念<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王陵</span>的恩德。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王陵</span>，就是<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">安国侯</span>。等到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张苍\">苍（张苍）</span>显贵，常像对待<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">父</span>亲一样侍奉<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王陵</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陵</span>死后，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张苍\">苍（张苍）</span>做<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>，休沐之日，常先去<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">朝</span>拜<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陵</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">夫人</span>，献上饮<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">食</span>，然后才敢回家。"
    },
    "14": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张苍\">苍（张苍）</span>做<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">十多年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">鲁</span>人<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公孙臣</span>上书说<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>为<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">土德</span>之时，其符应该有<span class=\"mythical\" title=\"神话\">黄龙</span>出现。诏下交给<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张苍</span>议论，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张苍</span>认为不对，就搁置了。后来<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">黄龙</span>出现在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">成纪</span>，于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉文帝\">文帝（汉文帝）</span>召<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公孙臣</span>任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">博士</span>，草拟<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">土德</span>的历<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">制度</span>，改<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">元年</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张苍\">张丞相（张苍）</span>由此自感不安，称病称老。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张苍\">苍（张苍）</span>举荐他人为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">中候</span>，那人大肆贪赃谋利，皇上为此责备<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张苍\">苍（张苍）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张苍\">苍（张苍）</span>就因病被免职。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张苍\">苍（张苍）</span>做<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">十五年（时长）</span>而被免。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉景帝\">孝景（汉景帝）</span>前<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">五年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张苍\">苍（张苍）</span>去世，谥为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：北平文侯\">文侯（北平文侯）</span>。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：北平康侯\">康侯（北平康侯）</span>继位，过了<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">八年（时长）</span>去世。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张类\">类（张类）</span>继位为侯，过了<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">八年（时长）</span>，因在<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>丧礼上就位不敬，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">国除</span>。"
    },
    "15": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "起初，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张苍</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">父</span>亲身高不满<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">五尺</span>，等生下<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张苍\">苍（张苍）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张苍\">苍（张苍）</span>身长<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">八尺馀</span>，做了<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">侯</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张苍\">苍（张苍）</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>也长高了。而到他的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">孙</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张类\">类（张类）</span>，身长<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">六尺</span>多，因犯<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">法</span>失去侯爵。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张苍\">苍（张苍）</span>被免<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相</span>后，年老，口中无齿，吃人<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">乳</span>，由<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">女</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>做<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">乳母</span>。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">妻妾</span>以百计，凡曾怀孕的就不再宠幸。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张苍\">苍（张苍）</span>活到<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">百多年（时长）</span>而卒。"
    },
    "16": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：申屠嘉\">申屠丞相（申屠嘉）</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">嘉</span>，是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>人，以<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">材官蹶张</span>的资格跟从<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘邦\">高帝（刘邦）</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：项羽\">项籍（项羽）</span>，升为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">队率</span>。跟随<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">黥布</span>军，任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">都尉</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝惠</span>时，任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">淮阳守</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝文帝</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">元年</span>，推举旧吏和<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">二千石</span>跟随过<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘邦\">高皇帝（刘邦）</span>的人，都封为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">关内侯</span>，食邑二十四人，而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">申屠嘉</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">食邑</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">五百户</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张苍</span>已任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">嘉</span>升任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">御史大夫</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张苍</span>免<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝文帝</span>想用<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">皇后</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">弟</span>弟<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">窦广国</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>，说：\"恐怕<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>认为我偏私<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">广国</span>。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">广国</span>贤明有德行，所以想以他为相，考虑了很久不妥，而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘邦\">高帝（刘邦）</span>时的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大臣</span>又多已亡故，剩下的看不到可用之人，就以<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">御史大夫</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">嘉</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>，因其原有食邑封为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">故安侯</span>。"
    },
    "17": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">嘉</span>为人清廉耿直，家门不接受私人谒见。 此时<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太中大夫</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">邓通</span>正得宠幸，赏赐累积巨万。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉文帝\">文帝（汉文帝）</span>曾在<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">通</span>家里宴饮，宠爱竟至如此。 此时<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>入朝，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">通</span>坐在皇上旁边，有怠慢的<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍·规范：礼\">礼记（礼）</span>节。 <span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>奏事完毕，趁便说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>宠爱<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">幸臣</span>，就让他<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">富贵</span>起来；但朝廷的<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍·规范：礼\">礼记（礼）</span>数，不可不严肃！\" 皇上说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>不要说了，我自己私下责备他。\" 退朝后坐在丞相府中，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">嘉</span>写<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">檄</span>文召<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">邓通</span>到<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相府</span>来，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">通</span>不来，就要<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">斩</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">通</span>。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">通</span>恐惧，入宫告诉<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉文帝\">文帝（汉文帝）</span>。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉文帝\">文帝（汉文帝）</span>说：\"你只管前去，我随即派人去召你。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">通</span>到<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相府</span>，摘下官冠，赤足，叩首谢罪。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">嘉</span>端坐自如，故意不以<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍·规范：礼\">礼记（礼）</span>相待，责备说：\"那朝廷，是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘邦\">高皇帝（刘邦）</span>的朝廷。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">通</span>是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">小臣</span>，竟在殿上戏谑，大不敬，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">当斩</span>。吏现在就去<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">斩</span>他！\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">通</span>叩首，叩得头上流出<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">血</span>，仍不能解。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉文帝\">文帝（汉文帝）</span>估计<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>已经困住<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">通</span>，便派使者持<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">节</span>去召<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">通</span>，对<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>说：\"这是我的弄<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>放了他。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">邓通</span>到后，对<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉文帝\">文帝（汉文帝）</span>哭道：\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>差点<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>了<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>。\""
    },
    "18": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">嘉</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">五年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝文帝</span>崩，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉景帝\">孝景帝（汉景帝）</span>即位。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">晁错</span>任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">内史</span>，受宠信而主事，对诸多<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">法令</span>都请求变更，议论以谴罚去削弱<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>。而<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">嘉</span>对自己所言不被采用感到不满，痛恨<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：晁错\">错（晁错）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：晁错\">错（晁错）</span>任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">内史</span>时，门开在东边，出入不便，就另开了一门朝南。南边门外是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太上皇</span>庙的外墙。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">嘉</span>听说后，想借此依<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">法</span>惩办<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：晁错\">错（晁错）</span>擅自穿<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">宗庙</span>墙开门，上奏请<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：晁错\">错（晁错）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：晁错\">错（晁错）</span>有门客告诉了<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：晁错\">错（晁错）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：晁错\">错（晁错）</span>恐惧，连夜入宫请谒，向<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">景帝</span>自首。到朝时，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>奏请<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">内史</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：晁错\">错（晁错）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">景帝</span>说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：晁错\">错（晁错）</span>所穿的不是真正的<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">庙垣</span>，而是外面的宫墙，所以别的官员也住在里面，况且又是我让他这么做的，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：晁错\">错（晁错）</span>无罪。\" 罢朝后，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">嘉</span>对<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">长史</span>说：\"我后悔没有先<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">斩</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：晁错\">错（晁错）</span>，反而先奏请，被<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：晁错\">错（晁错）</span>出卖了。\" 到家后，因此吐<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">血</span>而死。谥为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：故安节侯\">节侯（故安节侯）</span>。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：故安共侯\">共侯（故安共侯）</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蔑</span>继位，<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">三年（时长）</span>卒。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">侯</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：申屠去病\">去病（申屠去病）</span>继位，<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">三十一年（时长）</span>卒。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">侯</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：申屠臾\">臾（申屠臾）</span>继位，过了<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">六年（时长）</span>，因任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">九江太守</span>收受故官送礼有罪，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">国除</span>。"
    },
    "19": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "自<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">申屠嘉</span>死后，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">景帝</span>时有<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">开封侯</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陶青</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">桃侯</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">刘舍</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>。到了<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">今上</span>时，有<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">柏至侯</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">许昌</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">平棘侯</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">薛泽</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">武彊侯</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">庄青翟</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">高陵侯</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">赵周</span>等为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>。都以<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">列侯</span>身份继承爵位，谨小慎微，为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>不过充数而已，没有什么能显著于当世的功名建树。"
    },
    "20": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太史公</span>说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张苍</span>懂<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">文学</span>、<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">律历</span>，是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>名相，却驳斥<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">贾生</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公孙臣</span>等关于<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">正朔服色</span>的建议而不采纳，明显使用<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>的<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">颛顼历</span>，为什么呢？<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周昌</span>，是木讷刚强的人。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">任敖</span>因旧德而被任用。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">申屠嘉</span>可说是刚毅守节了，但无学术，大概与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：萧何\">萧（萧何）</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曹参\">曹（曹参）</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈平</span>是不同的。"
    },
    "21": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉武帝\">孝武（汉武帝）</span>时<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>很多，不曾记载，没有记录他们的言行起居，姑且记叙<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">征和</span>以来的事。"
    },
    "22": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "有<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：车千秋\">车丞相（车千秋）</span>，是<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">长陵</span>人。去世后由<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韦贤\">韦丞相（韦贤）</span>接替。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韦贤\">韦丞相（韦贤）</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">贤</span>，是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">鲁</span>人。凭读书学术做官，至<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">大鸿胪</span>。有相面之人给他看相，说当做到<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>。他有四个儿子，让相面之人给他们看相，看到第二个<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>，名叫<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">玄成</span>。相面的说：\"此<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>高贵，当封侯。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韦贤\">韦丞相（韦贤）</span>说：\"我如果做了<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>，有<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">长子</span>在，怎么能轮到他？\" 后来果然做了<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>，病死，而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">长子</span>因罪获论，不能继承，于是<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">玄成</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">玄成</span>当时佯装发狂，不肯立，最终还是立了他，有让国之名。后因骑马至庙，不敬，有诏<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">夺爵</span>一级，降为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">关内侯</span>，失去<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">列侯</span>，仍得食其原来国邑。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韦贤\">韦丞相（韦贤）</span>卒，由<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏相\">魏丞相（魏相）</span>继任。"
    },
    "23": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏相\">魏丞相（魏相）</span>，是<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">济阴</span>人。以文吏身份升至<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>。此人好武，让所有官吏都佩<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">剑</span>，佩<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">剑</span>上前奏事。有不佩<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">剑</span>的，要入奏时，就借<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">剑</span>才敢入奏。当时<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">京兆尹</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">赵</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>奏请[免罪，派人扣住<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏相\">魏丞相（魏相）</span>，想求脱罪，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏相\">魏丞相（魏相）</span>不听。又派人威胁恐吓<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏相\">魏丞相（魏相）</span>，借丞相<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">夫人</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>婢女之事，私下单独奏请查验。发吏卒到<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>府，逮捕奴婢<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">笞</span>打<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">审</span>问，查实并非以<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">兵刃</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>的。而<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">司直</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">繁</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>上奏说<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">京兆尹</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">赵</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>逼迫<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>，诬告说<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">夫人</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>婢女，发吏卒<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">围</span>捕<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>府，属大不道；又查得擅自屏退<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">骑士</span>之事，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">赵</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">京兆</span>判处腰<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">斩</span>。又有派<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">掾</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈平</span>等弹劾<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">中尚书</span>，疑以独自擅行劫迫之事而判罪，属大不敬，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">长史</span>以下都判死罪，有的下<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">蚕室</span>受刑。而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏相\">魏丞相（魏相）</span>最终以<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>身份病死。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>继承爵位。后因骑马至庙，不敬，有诏<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">夺爵</span>一级，降为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">关内侯</span>，失去<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">列侯</span>，仍得食其原来国邑。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏相\">魏丞相（魏相）</span>卒，由<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">御史大夫</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">邴吉</span>继任。"
    },
    "24": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：邴吉\">邴丞相（邴吉）</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吉</span>，是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">鲁</span>国人。凭读书好<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">法令</span>升至<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">御史大夫</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉宣帝\">孝宣帝（汉宣帝）</span>时，因有旧日情谊，封为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">列侯</span>，因而任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>。通晓政事，极有大智，后世称颂他。以<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>身份病死。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">显</span>继承爵位。后因骑马至庙，不敬，有诏<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">夺爵</span>一级，失去<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">列侯</span>，仍得食原国邑。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">显</span>做官至<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太仆</span>，因官<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">毛</span>管理混乱，本人及<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">子男</span>犯贪赃罪，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">免</span>为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">庶人</span>。"
    },
    "25": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：邴吉\">邴丞相（邴吉）</span>卒，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：黄霸\">黄丞相（黄霸）</span>继任。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">长安</span>中有个善于相面的<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田文</span>，与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韦贤\">韦丞相（韦贤）</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏相\">魏丞相（魏相）</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：邴吉\">邴丞相（邴吉）</span>在微贱时相会于客人家，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田文</span>说：\"如今这三位<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>，都是<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>。\" 其后<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三人</span>果然相继为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>，这种预见真是精明啊。"
    },
    "26": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：黄霸\">黄丞相（黄霸）</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">霸</span>，是<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">淮阳</span>人。以读书做官，至<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">颍川太守</span>。治理<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">颍川</span>，以<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">礼义</span>和条教来告谕教化。犯<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">法</span>的人，委婉晓谕令其<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">自杀</span>。教化<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">大行</span>，名声远扬。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉宣帝\">孝宣帝（汉宣帝）</span>下制书说：\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">颍川太守</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">霸</span>，宣布诏令治理<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">民</span>众，道不拾遗，男<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">女</span>分道而行，狱中没有重囚。<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">赐爵</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">关内侯</span>，<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">黄金</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">百斤</span>。\" 征召为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">京兆尹</span>而至<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>，又以<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">礼义</span>治理。以<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>身份病死。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>继承爵位，后做<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">列侯</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：黄霸\">黄丞相（黄霸）</span>卒，以<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">御史大夫</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">于定国</span>继任。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：于定国\">于丞相（于定国）</span>已有<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">廷尉</span>的传，在<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">张廷尉</span>的记载中。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：于定国\">于丞相（于定国）</span>离任后，由<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">御史大夫</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">韦玄成</span>继任。"
    },
    "27": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韦贤\">韦丞相（韦贤）</span>的子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">玄成</span>，就是前面<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韦贤\">韦丞相（韦贤）</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>。继承<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">父</span>爵，后来失了<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">列侯</span>。他年少时好读书，通晓<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍·规范：诗\">诗经（诗）</span>、<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">论语</span>。做官至<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">卫尉</span>，改任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太子太傅</span>。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">御史大夫</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">薛</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>免职后，他任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">御史大夫</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：于定国\">于丞相（于定国）</span>告老退职，他任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>，因故邑封为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">扶阳侯</span>。过了<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">数年（时长）</span>，病死。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉元帝\">孝元帝（汉元帝）</span>亲临丧礼，赏赐十分丰厚。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>继承爵位。他的施政随世俗浮沉，被人说是谄媚巧佞。而相面的人本说他当为侯代<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">父</span>，后来失去了；再次从游宦而起，至<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">父子</span>都做<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>，世间传为美谈，岂不是命吗！相面的人预先知道了。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韦贤\">韦丞相（韦贤）</span>卒，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">御史大夫</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">匡衡</span>继任。"
    },
    "28": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">匡衡</span>，是<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">东海</span>人。好读书，跟从<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">博士</span>学<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍·规范：诗\">诗经（诗）</span>。家贫，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">衡</span>靠给人做工来供<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">食</span>饮。才能低下，多次射策不中，到第九次，才中丙科。对经书因不能中科而更加熟悉。补为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">平原文学卒史</span>。过了<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">数年（时长）</span>，郡中并不尊敬他。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">御史</span>征召他，补为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">百石</span>属官，被举荐为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">郎</span>，而补为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">博士</span>，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">拜</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太子少傅</span>，事奉<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉元帝\">孝元帝（汉元帝）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉元帝\">孝元（汉元帝）</span>喜好<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍·规范：诗\">诗经（诗）</span>，因而升他为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">光禄勋</span>，居殿中做老师，向左右讲授，皇上也坐在旁边听，非常赞许他，地位日益尊贵。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">御史大夫</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">郑弘</span>因事被免，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：匡衡\">匡（匡衡）</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>升任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">御史大夫</span>。过了<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">一年多（时长）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韦贤\">韦丞相（韦贤）</span>死，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：匡衡\">匡（匡衡）</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>代他为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>，封<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">乐安侯</span>。在<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十年</span>之间，没走出<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">长安</span><span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">城门</span>一步而至<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>，这岂不是遇时而命啊！"
    },
    "39": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太史公</span>说：深思<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>人游宦以至封侯，实在微妙至极。然而多有至<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">御史大夫</span>就止步不前的。那些身为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大夫</span>则<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>是次升之位，其心里都盼望<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>死去。有的竟至于暗地里互相诋毁陷害，想取代他。然而守候职位<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">日</span>久而不得，有的任职<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">日</span>少而得之，至于封侯，真是命啊！<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">御史大夫</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：郑弘\">郑（郑弘）</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>守了<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">数年（时长）</span>不得，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：匡衡\">匡（匡衡）</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>在位不满一年，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韦贤\">韦丞相（韦贤）</span>死，他就代替了，岂能靠智谋巧计得到呢！怀有贤圣之才，困厄而不得的人非常多啊。"
    },
    "40": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张苍</span>任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">主计</span>，为<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>制定规程。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：公孙臣\">孙臣（公孙臣）</span>最初受黜，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>历仍行。 <span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">御史</span>位亚丞相，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相国</span>如<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：伊尹\">阿衡（伊尹）</span>。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：申屠嘉\">申屠（申屠嘉）</span>当面指责，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：周昌\">周子（周昌）</span>廷上谏争。 其他诸相拘谨小心，没有什么建树。"
    }
  }
}